Package lazyTrees

Class LazySearchTree<E extends java.lang.Comparable<? super E>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • lazyTrees.LazySearchTree<E>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Cloneable
    public class LazySearchTree<E extends java.lang.Comparable<? super E>>
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Cloneable
    Binary search tree (BST) that uses lazy deletion and also has functionality of hard deletion using collectGarbage().
    Author:
    Foothill College, Veronika Cabalova Joseph
